@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### RAG ingest document - Controller and Service commented out for perhaps future resurrection. 
### If brought back ReadMe.md should be updated to reflect this.
### For ElasticSearch RAG Ingest use later, navigate to http://localhost:5601/app/dev_tools and run "PUT /spring-ai-document-index"
### Note: Download sample PDF from https://www.terma.com/media/nf3ewqzn/employee-code-of-conduct-jan-2021.pdf
# POST {{baseUrl}}/rag/ingest
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary
# 
# --WebAppBoundary
# Content-Disposition: form-data; name="path"; filename="employee-code-of-conduct-jan-2021.pdf"
# Content-Type: application/pdf
# 
# < ./path/to/employee-code-of-conduct-jan-2021.pdf
# --WebAppBoundary--
#

### RAG models
GET {{baseUrl}}/rag/models

### RAG query - Anti-Corruption Policy
# GET {{baseUrl}}/rag/query?question=Give%20me%20detailed%20information%20on%20Anti-Corruption%20Policy

### RAG advised query - Multiple topics
# GET {{baseUrl}}/rag/advised?question=Give%20me%20detailed%20information%20on%20Ethical%20Decision%20Tree,%20Drugs%20and%20a%20Tobacco%20-%20Free%20Environment%20in%20the%20Workplace

### Policy RAG ingest from GCS policies/ prefix
POST {{baseUrl}}/rag/policies/ingest-gcs?prefix=policies/

### Policy RAG query with retrieval tuning
GET {{baseUrl}}/rag/policies/query?question=What%20are%20the%20rules%20for%20personal%20use%20of%20company%20email?&topK=5&similarityThreshold=0.6
